trans-unit.source: Enumerates values for levels of emphasis in prompts.
trans-unit.target: Nummererer verdier for nivåer i utheving i instruksjonene.

trans-unit.source: Members of the PromptEmphasis enumeration are used by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle.%23ctor%2A> constructor, by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.AppendText%2A> method, and by the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.StartStyle%2A> method to specify the level of emphasis for spoken text.
trans-unit.target: Medlemmer av PromptEmphasis-opplisting som brukes av den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle.%23ctor%2A>konstruktøren, av den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.AppendText%2A>metoden, og ved den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.StartStyle%2A>metode for å angi hvor mange utheving for talt tekst.</xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.StartStyle%2A> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder.AppendText%2A> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle.Emphasis%2A> property gets the emphasis for a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle> object using a PromptEmphasis instance.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle.Emphasis%2A>egenskapen henter vekten for en <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle>objekt med en forekomst av PromptEmphasis.</xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle> </xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptStyle.Emphasis%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The speech synthesis engines in Windows do not support variations in the emphasis of speech output at this time.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Tale syntese motorer i Windows støtter ikke variasjoner i Fremheving av taleutdata på dette tidspunktet.

trans-unit.source: Setting values for emphasis using a member of the PromptEmphasis enumeration will produce no audible change in the synthesized speech output.
trans-unit.target: Angi verdier for utheving ved hjelp av et medlem av PromptEmphasis opplistingen produsere ingen lyd endring i syntetisert tale utdataene.

trans-unit.source: Indicates a moderate level of emphasis.
Indicates that no emphasis value is specified.
trans-unit.target: Angir at ingen utheving-verdi er angitt.

trans-unit.source: Indicates a reduced level of emphasis.
Indicates a strong level of emphasis.
